::KitKat::

She watched at Drillbit came over to them. "AH, Drillbit. Please meet 
our latest edition to our team, Drillbit, this is Killfest. Killfest, 
please meet Drillbit. He's my main right hand bot around here."

Actually, he wasn't. But she couldn't make Drillbit feel bad infront 
of the new arrivals. She really wanted to make Drillbit second in 
command, but with ehr feelings for him, she couldn't allow the risk 
of being compromised in that manner.
